    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a methodology for benchmarking Segment Routing
   (SR) performance for Segment Routing over IPv6 (SRv6) and MPLS (SR-
   MPLS).  It builds upon RFC 2544, RFC 5180, RFC 5695 and RFC 8402.

